remain a resource and partner in your personal and professional journeys.       Follow us:     Follow us:       Follow us:           Google Maps image     Office of the Vice Chancellor for Advancement   601 S. Morgan Street,  University Hall,  100,  Chicago,  Illinois  60607    Phone: 312-413-8517  Email: advance@uic.edu             About Advancement    Back to main content           Directory     Central Advancement Leadership    Advancement Services    College and Unit Officers    Communications and Donor Relations    Corporate and Foundation Relations    Gift Planning    Participation    UIC Alumni Association    Major Gift Officers      Connect to College    Advancement Careers     FAQ    Benefits               Support IGNITE Campaign  Give now to IGNITE the future.  All gifts to UIC support IGNITE: The Campaign for UIC.      Volunteer  Share volunteer opportunities that would be most meaningful to you.      Update Your Information  Tell us where to send news and updates and how you'd like to engage.      Contact the UIC Alumni Association  Ask questions, share thought.  We want to hear from you!                 UIC Logo        Advancement       Contact   601 S. Morgan Street, 2503 University Hall (MC 002), Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: 312-413-8272  advance@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                  